    <div type="semanticcomponents">
        <!-- PREMIS Semantic components -->
        <p>None</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="definition">
        <!-- PREMIS Definition -->
        <p>The use(s) supported by the related environment.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="rationale">
        <!-- PREMIS Rationale -->
        <p>Different environments can support different uses of objects. For
            example, the environment needed to edit and modify a file can be quite
            different from the environment needed to render it.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="usagenotes">
        <!-- PREMIS Usage notes -->
        <p>Other values might indicate the ability to transform, print, and
            manipulate by program.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div type="datatype">
