        <p>Values should be taken from a controlled vocabulary. A controlled
            vocabulary is available at:
            <ref target="http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/preservation/environmentPurpose">http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/preservation/environmentPurpose</ref>.</p>
    </div>
    
